<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/476630-is-this-novel-full-of-gory-details-i-m">Is this novel full of gory details? I&#39;m not particularly squeamish. Ken Follett is one of my favorite authors and his stuff has some graphic descriptions of violence. Still, I don&#39;t want to read page after page of evisceration and torture.</a>
</div>
