<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">The book is full of scenes of violence, some of that are really disgusting, but they&apos;re written in a very natural style and don&apos;t go deep. I mean, Win<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">The book is full of scenes of violence, some of that are really disgusting, but they're written in a very natural style and don't go deep. I mean, Winslow didnt't a morbid style, don't expect something like American Psycho for example. <a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
