              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer12526120095801261058">Absolutely phenomenal. I’m reminded of Empire magazine’s Neil Jeffries who, in his five star review for Sling Blade, ends the review with this: “And it will make you think long and hard about the last time you saw a movie this good.” <br/><br/>Replace “saw a movie” with “read a book”. That’s Power of the Dog.</span>

          </span>
