<div class='bookAuthorProfile__about'>

<span id="freeTextContainer11141898938082906777">Don Winslow is the author of twenty-one acclaimed, award-winning international bestsellers, including the <i>New York Times</i> bestsellers <i>The Force</i> and <i>The Border</i>, the #1 international bestseller <i>The Cartel, The Power of the Dog, Savages</i>, and <i>The Winter of Frankie Machine</i>. <i>Savages</i> was made into a feature film by three-time Oscar-winning writer-director Oliver Stone. <i>The Power of the Dog, The Cartel</i> and</span>
  <span id="freeText11141898938082906777" style="display:none">Don Winslow is the author of twenty-one acclaimed, award-winning international bestsellers, including the <i>New York Times</i> bestsellers <i>The Force</i> and <i>The Border</i>, the #1 international bestseller <i>The Cartel, The Power of the Dog, Savages</i>, and <i>The Winter of Frankie Machine</i>. <i>Savages</i> was made into a feature film by three-time Oscar-winning writer-director Oliver Stone. <i>The Power of the Dog, The Cartel</i> and <i>The Border</i> sold to FX in a major multimillion-dollar deal to air as a weekly television series beginning in 2020. <br /><br />A former investigator, antiterrorist trainer and trial consultant, Winslow lives in California and Rhode Island.<br /><br /><br /><i>Librarian Note: There is more than one author in the GoodReads database with this name. <a href="https://www.goodreads.com/topic/show_group/44217.Master_List_of_Author_Disambiguation_by_Spaces" rel="nofollow noopener">See this thread for more information</a>.</i><br /></span>
